{"tid":425803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁孔德指昨晚噓國歌情況有改善 梁美芬：立法後就不容許","createTime":"2017-10-06T04:55:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-06T05:47:42.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"837d1a746e59ea04ef154b5439b1e41fa86cd70c","tid":425803,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T04:55:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20171006/large/1507262185_d2d4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171006%2Flarge%2F1507262185_d2d4.jpg&h=bdb8f8aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【更新內容】<br />\n香港足球代表隊昨晚在旺角場友賽老撾，2,239名球迷到場觀戰，賽前奏國歌時，北看台有部分球迷發出噓聲，噓聲不算太大，亦有人背向草地及舉「中指」，當時在場觀戰的足總行政總薛基輔未有對球迷繼續噓國歌作回應。香港足總主席梁孔德今早在電台節目指，球迷噓國歌的情況，已較早前世界盃外圍賽時有改善。梁表示，比賽前無可避免要奏國歌，足總無辦法控制球迷的行動，亦無法估計亞洲足協的行動。<br />\n<br />\n足總副主席貝鈞奇透露，亞洲足協昨日有代表監場，要視乎他們撰寫的賽事報告才決定如何處理。貝鈞奇指足總不希望發生類似事件，認為不適宜在球場上以此方法表達對社會的不滿，呼籲球迷不要作出不尊重對賽球隊以及自己的行為。<br />\n<br />\n貝鈞奇強調球迷再次噓國歌，今次如有懲罰，可能會罰得比較重。對於內地已實施《國歌法》，而本港稍後亦會進行本地立法，貝鈞奇表示，足總會再詳細研究日後如何處理類似事件。<br />\n<br />\n經民聯立法會議員梁美芬認為，昨晚事件明顯是侮辱行為，相信本地就國歌法立法後，是不被容許的。她指本地制定國歌法期間，仍不斷有香港市民故意侮辱國歌，很容易令人認為要更加推動對國家的尊重，對於香港是不利。<br />\n<br />\n前年11月港足主場對國足的世界盃外圍賽中，有球迷向國歌報以噓聲，結果被國際足協罰款1萬瑞士法郎（約7.7萬港元），並指若有再犯，將面臨更嚴重處分。香港足總當時呼籲球迷在未來的比賽克制，避免足總及港足再被罰。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57297295&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171006\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57297295%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171006&d=Vw%2BPPaDukkvmVNujyjkxCDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=fef01020\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57297295%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171006&h=94e0d24b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57297295&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171006</a>"},{"pid":"d955f4071d7b35e42a2b2ad0bec7194e243626d0","tid":425803,"uid":15711,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T05:10:40.000Z","msg":"有骨氣既連登仔到時仲敢唔敢噓呢？"},{"pid":"790e5a80d17e11fa5b79248bbf695bfd4f710131","tid":425803,"uid":20816,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T05:12:09.000Z","msg":"祝梁美芬長命百歲但百病纏身"},{"pid":"139bc2b7ba04a2a981ec56c350a3da8021008b39","tid":425803,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T05:13:15.000Z","msg":"我又想知佢點樣檢控幾千人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2313ea2960a81c35a59ae4e1ad777c82dbd5e4d","tid":425803,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T05:14:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">夠薑咪告曬囉，佔中你告咗幾多個</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"247c06c4c04c2e83cb9bbc5d506573ccfc863f70","tid":425803,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T05:15:31.000Z","msg":"講到好似梁孔穩指揮人噓國歌咁"},{"pid":"b91ac142a0b1a71fa6d63ce1b689f62a0af6725a","tid":425803,"uid":2697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T05:16:08.000Z","msg":"如果立法後外籍球員點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cceef9e7cae27198cf3e2da655b59ae21da02ea4","tid":425803,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T05:16:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果立法後外籍球員點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要嘈中蝗語歌"},{"pid":"0257f42a7159c1354291687b80f089f944ae16cc","tid":425803,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T05:1